**🎲 Battle Formula:**
```javascript
Attack Power = (Base ATK × Soldiers) + Weapons + Buffs
Defense Power = (Base DEF × Wall Level) + Shields + Buffs

Win Probability = ATK / (ATK + DEF)
Loot = Enemy Treasury × (10-30%)
Casualties = (Soldiers × 20-40%) if lose
```

